<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>When used in a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-sequentialanimation.xml">SequentialAnimation</db:link>, <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-pauseanimation.xml">PauseAnimation</db:link> is a step when nothing happens, for a specified duration.</db:para>
<db:para>A 500ms animation sequence, with a 100ms pause between two animations:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">SequentialAnimation {
    NumberAnimation { ... duration: 200 }
    PauseAnimation { duration: 100 }
    NumberAnimation { ... duration: 200 }
}
</db:programlisting>
